Type: Package
Package: rsurveyjs
Title: SurveyJS Htmlwidget and Shiny Bindings
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Malte", "Grosser", , "malte.grosser@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Render SurveyJS forms in Shiny from JSON schemas. Provides an
    htmlwidget that emits final submissions and optional live updates,
    plus a server-side API to update answers, toggle read-only mode, and
    change theme or locale.
